<span id="freeTextContainer1596373332992089502">You know I only bought this book because I read the list of characters and couldn&apos;t make any sense of it. And I couldn&apos;t make any sense of where the book was going till about half way (and that&apos;s a lot of pages), although all the separate parts were completely fascinating. Then the bits gradually started to come together - and my head pretty much exploded with the brilliance of it all. Worth the wait, let me tell you.</span>
